description:
Anekawa Mone, a girl who exceled in both brains and beauty. She was almost flawless if not for her lack of stamina along with strength and because of that, she could not enjoy VR.

However, after sending an email of appeal to a newly released VRMMORPG, that issue was resolved.

This is the tale of how a girl who was perfect in all but her constitution, received a formidable body… as a shoggoth and tackled on the game world.>
